articles.author: David Kirton
articles.title: Huawei seeks to steal spotlight from Apple with launch of $2,800 tri-fold smartphone - Reuters
articles.description: China's Huawei Technologies on Tuesday unveiled a $2,800 tri-foldable phone as it seeks to extend its lead in the world's biggest smartphone market and steal the spotlight from Apple hours after it debuted a new iPhone.
